title: Embrace The Place Where You Are | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Embrace The Place Where You Are | Joel Osteen
description:
Too many people are living frustrated because they're trying to fight everything that's happening in their lives. Instead of worrying over the things you can't control, turn them over to God. You can trust Him even when you don't understand. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
